{"tid":278473,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"日本爆笑惡搞長輩圖！全球皆開始惡搞廢話...","createTime":"2017-06-10T13:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T05:10:55.000Z","uid":1886,"like":45,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3a459573df61a7f36785185108ee57c5e06ae0","tid":278473,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:10:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Nozgb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNozgb.png&h=9851899a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NoT16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNoT16.png&h=19e17f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iau0O9-J-E0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIau0O9-J-E0&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTz7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=bef01417\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iau0O9-J-E0</a></div><br />\n<br />\n港台過去流行一陣子認同請分享的「長輩圖」，內容多半是問候或是大家都知道的廢話，但對於初學即時通訊的長輩，轉傳這些圖片就變成了他們開啟話匣子的秘訣。台灣似乎就是走在這潮流的尖端，因為最近日本推特上才開始流行起「#あたりまえポエム」，這tag就是指著「理所當然的詩」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NoYrU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNoYrU.png&h=55646c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NoRlF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNoRlF.png&h=3bb238cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/No3mq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNo3mq.png&h=9de419a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170313/883443.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170313%2F883443.htm&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTz7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=62e76b93\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170313/883443.htm</a></div><br />\n<br />\n「#あたりまえポエム」就跟「長輩圖」一樣，擁有一張風景照加上一段話，乍看之下似乎充滿美感也具有意思，但想了一下，不就是句廢話嘛！如「在非洲，每一分鐘就有60秒過去」或是「看看每個駕駛座上的運醬，大家都是往前看喔！」，不禁讓網友這廢話等級根本就在浪費生命。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2389/2389291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2389%2F2389291.jpg&h=3cbe9776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「聽見你的名字時，會最先想到你臉的樣子」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2389/2389292.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2389%2F2389292.jpg&h=b2319095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「眼睛蒙上後，不知道為什麼就看不見了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2389/2389294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2389%2F2389294.jpg&h=745e9912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「我只想著你和你以外的事情！」（這招是用來哄騙初入社會的小妹妹嗎？）</div><br />\n<br />\n受到日式廢文影響，也有不少人直接發揮想像力留下「路就是一條直直的」、「你知道嗎？人類是可以喝岩漿的喔　可是只能喝一次」、「不管是電話那頭還是這頭，總有一邊會先掛」等廢文。但這些廢文無極限，出版商預計將全數收錄成冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並已經在4月正式推出，單行本定價1000元日幣，雖然價格不高，但好想知道購入這本廢話全冊的消費者都長怎樣喔！"},{"pid":"08ef17feee5e8f8971273aa7276fe43c86a9d14c","tid":278473,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a54be154781982e0a6544e898d0699a1b0a2d1","tid":278473,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NoCdH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNoCdH.png&h=5d8c6233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br /